</span></div>
        </li>
              <li>
          <div><div>  <a href="/blog/fiction/lucilla-anna-voltaggio" hreflang="en"><img loading="lazy" src="/sites/worldliteraturetoday.org/files/styles/medium_thumbnail/public/Voltaggio-Anchor.jpg?itok=OUrr0cFM" width="250" height="175" alt="A bright green sweater hanging on a wall painted sky blue with clouds" typeof="foaf:Image" class="img-fluid image-style-medium-thumbnail" />

